Table oms.Shop2Supplier2ReduceReasonDO

Reduction agreement of a shop-supplier relation which contains a relation of reduce reasons of both, shop and supplier.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id bigint PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
shopReduceReason varchar(50) The name of the reduce reason as used by the shop. Example "default" 
supplierReduceReason varchar(50) The name of the reduce reason as used by the supplier. Example "no reduction" 
Shop2SupplierDO shop2SupplierRef bigint NOT_NULL The relation of the shop and supplier the named reduce reasons should be used for. 
isDefault boolean NOT_NULL false Marks the default reduce relation for the shop-supplier relation.
